    "license": "Published instrument; original CAAS developed by Savickas & Porfeli (2012)",
    "stem": "Different people use different strengths to build their careers. No one is good at everything, each of us emphasizes some strengths more than others. Please rate how strongly you have developed each of the following abilities using the scale below."
